posts.description: Fruity cereal 🍓🍌🥛 Chop up whatever fruit you want and pour your favorite non-dairy milk alll over. I've been making lots of almond milk lately (so goood 😋). Top with chopped dates, shredded coconut, and coconut sugar. Add granola to make it extra tasty 💫
For those days where I really don't feel like cleaning out my juicer @juicefromtheraw 🍃 Kale, spinach, swisschard, romaine, celery, cucumber, ginger, lemon, and apple 🍏
Rice with veggies, over spinach + cilantro, with spicy tahini 🥑💫

Growing up, my mom would take me and my five younger siblings to farms to pick our own tomatoes, corn, peas, peppers, strawberries, blueberries, and grapes. We would get up just as the sun came up. For an hour or two, we filled up several buckets with fresh produce. This would later become salsa, jam, pies, soups, and juice. I'm so thankful to my mom taught me how to be patient and work hard. And for sharing her love of good food with me. Shopping for fresh produce makes me so happy because of how it reminds me of home 🏡

Pressed juices contain far more nutrients than smashing some fruits and veggies through my traditional juicer 🍎🥒🥕🍍 I've been drinking these raw juices from @juicefromtheraw for the past few days, and I have felt so GREAT 😍 Like jumping off the walls, energy coursing through me great 💃🏻 I decided to change it up a bit and use them in my ice cream. Is it surprising that it turned out delicious??? ~Coconut banana nicecream~
-3 or 4 frozen bananas, chopped
-1/4 cup Coconut Fusion juice
-1/2 cup shredded coconut
Blend in a high speed blender. ~Beetroot banana nicecream~
-3 or 4 frozen bananas
-1/4 cup Root Veggies juice
-1 tsp shredded beetroot 
Blend, blend, blend!

Top with kiwi and chopped pistachios. Or anything really. Go crazy 😜 💚
Who here enjoys eating raw vegetables??🙋🏻 Yeah me either 😝 Unless they are heavily dipped in something. Or wrapped in rice paper. Or both ⇧⇧ ❤️😋

Creamy smoothie bowls for momma + babe 💖🍨 I've always loved the combo of raspberries and chocolate. My husband (Brad), on the other hand, despises the fruit + chocolate combo. But hey, more for me 😌🍓🍫🍓🍫🍓🍫
Top your oatmeal with a pile of fresh fruit, homemade jam, and peanut butter. It's really good 👅❤️🍓

SUSHIRRITO 🌯😍💖 The recipe is up on @TheFeedFeed (link in bio 👆🏻). The combo of @EarthboundFarm's Asian salad kit, sweet potato, tofu, asparagus, and pickled cabbage...was perfect 👌🏻 The tofu was marinated in a tahini dressing before being covered in a crunchy mixture of sunflower seeds and toasted. Sound good?? It was 😋 #EarthboundFarm #TheFeedFeed #Partner

I've teamed up with @EarthboundFarm and @TheFeedFeed to bring you the vegan sushi burrito! 🌯🌯🌯 I used everything in this salad kit (tahini dressing, tortilla strips, sunflower seeds, salad) to take this meal to the next level 🔥 I'll be posting the recipe for this + overnight pickled cabbage tomorrow, so check back! #EarthboundFarm #TheFeedFeed #Partner
